<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;ve seen some confusion floating around about this so I figured I&apos;d hop on and clarify - Roma and Juliette are m/f! Of course, there&apos;s certainly on-p<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I've seen some confusion floating around about this so I figured I'd hop on and clarify - Roma and Juliette are m/f! Of course, there's certainly on-page LGBTQ+ rep for other main characters in the book.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
