  <span id="freeText15344815958248962966" style="display:none">Chloe Gong is the <i>New York Times</i> bestselling author of <i>These Violent Delights</i> and its sequel <i>Our Violent Ends</i>. She is a recent graduate of the University of Pennsylvania, where she double-majored in English and International Relations. Born in Shanghai and raised in Auckland, New Zealand, Chloe is now located in New York pretending to be a real adult. You can find her on Twitter, Instagram, and TikTok under @thechloegong.</span>
